WEBVTT

00:01.060 --> 00:06.430
Joining me right now is Shri Mataji and She
is known throughout the world as a saint.

00:06.430 --> 00:09.746
And that’s the first time that I have been
able to meet a saint.

00:09.746 --> 00:13.820
And you’re also a faith healer or psychic healer, I guess some
people call you.

00:13.820 --> 00:17.919
But when asked in a recent interview as to
whether or not you were a saint or considered

00:17.919 --> 00:22.040
yourself to be a saint, you had a very unusual
answer. Are you?

00:22.369 --> 00:27.580
Actually, you cannot certify yourself, isn’t
it, as anything?

00:27.580 --> 00:34.680
The quality of a saint is that he can make
other saints. If he can make others saints,

00:34.680 --> 00:38.440
then he’s a saint. Otherwise, it’s just
self-certification.

00:38.440 --> 00:40.889
Can you make other people saints?
- I think so.

00:40.889 --> 00:46.120
Yes. How would you define a saint or what would
another person become that would make him a saint?

00:46.283 --> 00:50.593
The person who becomes a saint develops a new awareness

00:50.593 --> 00:58.820
as a result of a living process
of evolution that he becomes the Spirit as

00:58.820 --> 01:02.575
described by Christ that: “You are to be
born again”.

01:02.575 --> 01:08.819
And in that, the awareness becomes: it's actualization. It’s not just mental projection but actualization,

01:09.020 --> 01:14.630
that you become a person who is Collectively Conscious.

01:14.630 --> 01:20.450
You mentioned Christ and yet you are from
an Eastern country being from India.

01:20.450 --> 01:22.022
Do you believe in Jesus Christ ?

01:22.022 --> 01:27.349
Of course, of course! He plays a very big role in your evolution. He is the gate as said.

01:27.490 --> 01:32.341
So then by your definition a saint could be
a person who might be a born-again Christian?

01:32.341 --> 01:36.210
Who might have taken the Collective
Consciousness of Jesus into their lives?

01:36.210 --> 01:40.245
You see, those who accept him mentally are
not born again.

01:40.245 --> 01:44.506
Though, it is a happening that has to take place.
Baptism is a happening.

01:44.506 --> 01:51.077
And that happening takes place when there’s a vital force within our sacrum bone which rises.

01:51.077 --> 01:57.600
You can actually feel the rising of that force it comes up
onto the fontanel bone area -where we baptize-

01:57.600 --> 02:00.249
and you feel the cool breeze of the Holy Ghost.

02:00.249 --> 02:02.799
Yes, they say that there’s a cool breeze.
-Breeze of the Holy Ghost

02:02.799 --> 02:03.799
That people feel.
-Yes

02:03.799 --> 02:09.001
And another of the interviews that I read
about you said that the interviewer who interviewed you

02:09.001 --> 02:12.319
that you put your hand above the interviewer.
-Yes.

02:12.319 --> 02:14.874
And he was able to also feel the cool breeze

02:14.874 --> 02:16.995
Yes, yes. And also, from the [hands]

02:17.002 --> 02:18.793
Can you give me the cool breeze?
I’ve been waiting all my life for that.

02:18.793 --> 02:20.330
Yes, I think you pass
-Yes, right?

02:20.330 --> 02:22.670
You were little upset in the beginning when
I saw you,

02:22.670 --> 02:24.430
I was upset this morning.
-And it’s all right.

02:24.430 --> 02:25.148
Yes.

02:25.148 --> 02:27.945
I think, but now you have cool down,
and it will work out in no time.

02:28.045 --> 02:29.400
So, will I get the cool breeze?
-Of course.

02:29.400 --> 02:30.599
Or do you have to touch me?

02:30.599 --> 02:35.765
No, no, no, no. It might help, talking to me,
you might get it, but actually, you feel it on your fingertips.

02:35.765 --> 02:41.254
As Muhammad Sahib has said that:
“At the time of Resurection, your hands will speak.”

02:41.254 --> 02:45.000
And for the first time
you feel that All-pervading subtle power,

02:45.000 --> 02:48.500
But you become something more than what you are.

02:48.500 --> 02:49.930
That’s the saint.

02:49.930 --> 02:54.909
You have healed many people how many would
you estimate they’ve healed in your lifetime?

02:54.909 --> 02:58.269
I don’t know how many, I’ve never kept
count out.

02:58.269 --> 02:59.420
Hundreds?
-Yes, at least.

02:59.420 --> 03:01.719
At least, at least hundreds.
-Yes, at least hundreds.

03:01.719 --> 03:04.989
But, actually, the people who become Saints
can also.

03:04.989 --> 03:12.150
So if you see Sahaja Yoga, it can be in thousands.
Because so many people who became prophets,

03:12.150 --> 03:13.150
they have done it.

03:13.150 --> 03:14.165
They are also healing other people.

03:14.165 --> 03:17.157
Yes, they are also. They are healing much more than myself nowadays.

03:17.270 --> 03:20.809
What type of diseases or things have you been
able to heal?

03:20.970 --> 03:24.739
Most of the incurable diseases get healed,
but it’s not a faith healing, in the sense

03:24.739 --> 03:28.759
you don’t have to have faith, or you don’t
have to believe into any things.

03:28.759 --> 03:33.579
There’s no blindness about it. There’s no blindness.
Actually, it’s a happening, as I told you,

03:33.579 --> 03:40.250
like a sprouting of the seed. As a seed sprouts,
in the same way, your awakening takes place.

03:40.250 --> 03:46.200
And by that, you get your parasympathetic nervous
system nourished. It’s a question of nourishment.

03:46.200 --> 03:49.730
Nourishment, that’s how it works out.

03:49.730 --> 03:55.150
