It’s rather difficult.

04:14.830 --> 04:18.180
Why? Why is it when he said so, why is it

04:18.180 --> 04:20.912
we cannot have those innocent eyes? We should
have!

04:20.912 --> 04:25.146
The reason is what he said that He is to be born again within you.”

04:25.146 --> 04:31.590
And there’s a specific place where
Christ is awakened when this force rises.

